  "texts": [
    "The algorithm then updates the frequency count for the matrix cells associated with the new row and column representing the new 2-gram.",
    "The row and column added after that will yield either 3-or 4-gram words (combinations of 1-grams and 2-grams or double 2-grams.)",
    "That is, some new tokens may be complete 3-gram words like the and 4-gram suffixes like ized.",
    "The BPE method has the capacity to encode a diverse range of languages and Unicode characters by efficiently capturing sub-word structure and distinct meaning across similar words.",
    "The method can also effectively tokenize out-of-vocabulary words so that the model can infer their meaning."
